OL,3,CMolly Russell would be fighting to
OL,4,Cmake online world safe, bereaved
OL,5,Cfather says
OL,7,FThe father of Molly Russell has said
OL,8,Fhis daughter would be fighting to make
OL,9,Fthe online world safe if she was still
OL,10,Falive, as he and other bereaved
OL,11,Fparents urged the Government to take
OL,12,Furgent action to tackle social media
OL,13,Fharms.
OL,15,FCampaigners, whose children's deaths
OL,16,Fwere linked to social media, were told
OL,17,Fduring a meeting with the Prime
OL,18,FMinister on Tuesday that measures to
OL,19,Fprotect youngsters should be announced
OL,20,Fin "weeks, not months".
OL,26,@|D@DOU|D@VO]
