OL,3,CMolly Russell would be fighting to
OL,4,Cmake online world safe, bereaved
OL,5,Cfather says
OL,7,FIt came ahead of the deadline for the
OL,8,FGovernment's consultation on what
OL,9,Faction it should take, titled Growing
OL,10,FUp In The Online World, which closed
OL,11,Fjust before midnight.
OL,13,FMore than 80,000 responses were
OL,14,Fsubmitted, including from more than
OL,15,F40,000 parents and 13,000 young
OL,16,Fpeople, and a raft of measures are
OL,17,Fbeing considered ` ranging from a ban
OL,18,Fon under-16s using social media to
OL,19,Flimiting scrolling or imposing
OL,20,Fovernight curfews for children.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
