OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779847404
OL,3,CMolly Russell would be fighting to
OL,4,Cmake online world safe, bereaved
OL,5,Cfather says
OL,7,FRemembering Molly as a "campaigner"
OL,8,Fwho stood up for what she believed was
OL,9,Fright, Mr Russell told the Press
OL,10,FAssociation: "Molly was a very
OL,11,Fordinary young person who just
OL,12,Fhappened to click on a few wrong
OL,13,Fthings on the internet and then the
OL,14,Falgorithms, which were brand new to
OL,15,Fthe world at the time, kicked in and
OL,16,Ffed her ever more stuff.
OL,18,F"She should still be here now, and if
OL,19,Fshe was she'd be fighting to make the
OL,20,Fdigital world as safe as possible for
OL,21,Fothers to use."
OL,26,@oD@XOUoD@cO]rD@NOUzD@AOU}D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
