OL,3,CMolly Russell would be fighting to
OL,4,Cmake online world safe, bereaved
OL,5,Cfather says
OL,7,FInstead of a ban, Mr Russell is urging
OL,8,Fthe Government to end engagement-based
OL,9,Falgorithms, infinite scroll and
OL,10,Fdisappearing messages for young
OL,11,Fpeople, as well as implement measures
OL,12,Fthat stop strangers from being able to
OL,13,Fcontact a child online.
OL,15,FHe said building safe platforms must
OL,16,Fbe "the price" of tech firms doing
OL,17,Fbusiness in the UK.
OL,19,F"We wouldn't let a car on our roads in
OL,20,Fthe UK without it passing our safety
OL,21,Fstandards," he told PA.
OL,26,@xD@DOUxD@NO]{D@AOU}D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
