OL,3,CMolly Russell would be fighting to
OL,4,Cmake online world safe, bereaved
OL,5,Cfather says
OL,7,F"I don't see why we shouldn't learn
OL,8,Fthe lessons from our offline world and
OL,9,Fapply similar rules and regulations to
OL,10,Fthe online world."
OL,12,FEllen Roome, who believes her son
OL,13,FJools Sweeney died aged 14 after
OL,14,Flooking at harmful content online,
OL,15,Fsaid outside Number 10 on Tuesday
OL,16,Fafternoon: "I pushed quite hard on why
OL,17,Fhaven't they done something now, and
OL,18,Fthis whole thing around the
OL,19,Fconsultation was because various
OL,20,Fcharities have said they need to
OL,21,Fconsider their views.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@RO]xD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
