OL,3,CMolly Russell would be fighting to
OL,4,Cmake online world safe, bereaved
OL,5,Cfather says
OL,7,FChair of the committee, Helen Hayes,
OL,8,Fsaid: "From bullying and misogyny to
OL,9,Fabuse and sexual exploitation,
OL,10,Fchildren and young people growing up
OL,11,Ftoday face a deluge of serious harms
OL,12,Fwhenever they log on to social media."
OL,14,FA survey on 13- to 20-year-olds'
OL,15,Fexperiences of online misogyny,
OL,16,Fconducted in March by Censuswide for
OL,17,Fchildren's charity Barnardo's, found a
OL,18,Fquarter of girls have been called
OL,19,Fdegrading names online.
OL,26,@pD@GOUtD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
