OL,3,CMolly Russell would be fighting to
OL,4,Cmake online world safe, bereaved
OL,5,Cfather says
OL,7,FEarlier on Tuesday, Sir Keir Starmer
OL,8,Fsaid he has tasked the Government with
OL,9,Fputting together "a game-changer"
OL,10,Fpolicy to ensure children's safety
OL,11,Fonline, pledging action will be
OL,12,Fcarried out "very quickly".
OL,14,FVisiting a nursery school in East
OL,15,FSussex, Sir Keir said: "We will be
OL,16,Fdecisive, because it's absolutely
OL,17,Fclear to me that we need to take
OL,18,Faction to protect children, and we can
OL,19,Fact quickly."
OL,26,@qD@ROUqD@aO]tD@MOUtD@ZO]wD@XOU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
